---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <BaseHead title={"3. Cryptids & Biological Anomalies | " + SITE_TITLE} description="3. Cryptids & Biological Anomalies category page" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <main class="category-page" style="width: 75%; max-width: none; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <header style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
            <h1>3. Cryptids & Biological Anomalies</h1>
        </header>

        <section class="category-article" style="margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
            <p>Cryptids like the Mothman, Bigfoot, or the Chupacabra represent the bridge between folklore and pseudoscience. These legends often manifest in specific geographic regions, acting as modern "monsters" that haunt the fringes of civilization. This dimension analyzes the eyewitness phenomenon and the cultural specificities of cryptids. For example, the Mothman is tied to disaster omens, while the Chupacabra reflects local agricultural anxieties. These stories persist because they satisfy our desire for mystery in an overly mapped world.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="category-wp-content">
<figure class="wp-block-uagb-image__figure"><img decoding="async" src="/media-images/posts/mothman-sightings-history-illustration-1.webp" alt="Illustration for 3. Cryptids & Biological Anomalies" class="uag-image-1353" width="1200" height="450" title="3. Cryptids & Biological Anomalies" loading="lazy" role="img"></figure>
</section>



<section class="category-keywords" style="margin: 40px 0; padding: 20px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.3rem;">Related Keywords</h3>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px;">
        <a href="/blog/cryptids-vs-urban-legends-differences-mothman/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #B91C1C); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 0.95rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; border: 1px solid #fff; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#cryptids vs urban legends differences</a>
        <a href="/blog/historical-evidence-of-the-mothman/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #B91C1C); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 0.95rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; border: 1px solid #fff; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#historical evidence of the mothman</a>
        <a href="/blog/local-legends-of-cryptids-map-analysis/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #B91C1C); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 0.95rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; border: 1px solid #fff; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#local legends of cryptids map</a>
        <a href="/blog/biological-explanation-for-cryptid-sightings/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #B91C1C); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 0.95rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; border: 1px solid #fff; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#biological explanation for cryptid sightings</a>
        <a href="/blog/cultural-impact-of-cryptozoology/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #B91C1C); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 0.95rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; border: 1px solid #fff; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#cultural impact of cryptozoology</a>
    </div>
</section>




        


<div class="category-faq-section" style="margin-top: 60px; padding: 40px 30px; background: #1A1816; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(185,28,28,0.4);">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; color: #E8E2D5; font-size: 2rem; font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-content" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px;">

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #E8E2D5; border-radius: 4px; padding: 24px; border-left: 3px solid var(--accent, #B91C1C); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--accent-dark, #7A1212); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;">Q: Are cryptids real?</h4>
            <p style="color: #2A2723; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> No scientific proof yet</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #E8E2D5; border-radius: 4px; padding: 24px; border-left: 3px solid var(--accent, #B91C1C); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--accent-dark, #7A1212); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;">Q: Mothman location?</h4>
            <p style="color: #2A2723; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Point Pleasant, WV</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #E8E2D5; border-radius: 4px; padding: 24px; border-left: 3px solid var(--accent, #B91C1C); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--accent-dark, #7A1212); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;">Q: What is cryptozoology?</h4>
            <p style="color: #2A2723; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Study of hidden animals</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #E8E2D5; border-radius: 4px; padding: 24px; border-left: 3px solid var(--accent, #B91C1C); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--accent-dark, #7A1212); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;">Q: Why call them omens?</h4>
            <p style="color: #2A2723; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Linked to historical disasters</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #E8E2D5; border-radius: 4px; padding: 24px; border-left: 3px solid var(--accent, #B91C1C); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: var(--accent-dark, #7A1212); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;">Q: Famous cryptid list?</h4>
            <p style="color: #2A2723; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Bigfoot, Loch Ness, Yeti</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
    </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
